title: The Recording Revolution JumpStart To Editing TU70R1AL - UGET
description:
A good mix is only as good as the edited tracks. From tightening up multitrack drums, to locking bass, guitars, keys, and vocals in the pocket, JumpStart To Editing makes it easy, no matter what software you are using. I show you my typical editing workflow on a full production so you can see how I get my tracks to sound clean, polished, and in time, every time!
